com.apriori.di

Interface Binding

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractBinding

    public interface Binding
    A set of bindings to be used during code generation. Classes that implement this interface are not intended to be used at application runtime but are only used by the DI tools to generate other artifacts that the application will use.
